    <ul>
      <li parentName="ul">{`An exception thrown by try block is caught by the catch block. A try block must have at least one catch, though there can be many catch block for catching different types of exceptions. A catch block must have a try block prior written which will throw an exception. The catch block is used as :`}</li>
